strInstruct=   instructions     notice the tally counter under the scoreboard?  this number increments as you drop tiles on the board  be sure that the tally counter holds the right number to be scored before pressing the submit button for each players turn  if for some reason you have shuffled the tiles too much on the board making the tally counter error then just press the clear tally button to start over  now begin clicking each tile the correct number of times to tally your score then press submit to add your score to the scoreboard